snippet.title: 'Aquaman': Amber Heard interview
snippet.description:
Amber Heard talks about playing Mera in 'Aquaman' and her experience working with director James Wan in this interview with Yahoo Entertainment. Heard also explains how this "isn't a classic formulaic approach to a superhero movie"  and why she's excited for young girls to watch this film. #Aquaman #AmberHeard
